snippet.title: FragHero
snippet.description:
Exclusive gameplay, epic action and funny gaming videos. That's what you'll get here. 

If you're a fan of shooting video games and action games, you're gonna love FragHero. 

We're all about that mix of skilful shots with a twist of teammate banter and funny gameplay fails thrown in. 

Our hero series Top Frags of the Week gives you a chance to showcase your epic killcams and gameplay to the gaming community. Submit your clips at fraghero.com or facebook.com/groups/FragHeroes/ to be featured. 

Tune in Thursdays & Saturdays for new videos

FragHero is a Social Chain Media brand.
